React lifecycle hook that runs an effect only once.

## Usage

```tsx


const Demo = () => {
  useEffectOnce(() => {
    console.log("Running effect once on mount");

    return () => {
      console.log("Running clean-up of effect on unmount");
    };
  });

  return null;
};
```

